│   }                                                                                                                                                                                      │
│ // ...                                                                                                                                                                                   │
│ ```                                                                                                                                                                                      │
│ This check will prevent the transformation in this case, as `Idx` (1) is equal to `Op1Idx` (1). This seems correct and safe.                                                             │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ I will apply this patch.                                                                                                                                                                 │
│                                                                                                                                                                                          │
│ ```bash                                                                                                                                                                                  │
